   The stock market moved sharply lower today,
weighed down by weakness in bond prices and futures-related selling.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials tumbled 28.55 to 2,474.81
by 3 p.m. on Wall Street.
   Declining issues outpaced advances by a wide margin, with 1,084
